quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,49,"Maaku: "Goonga ka arii [Iislaamu on], mehre [ke'eferaagu] ngu alaa ka feeña, kadi, nde ruttotaako"."
  34,50,"Maaku: "Si mi majjii, haray ko hoore-am mi majjani; si mi feewii kadi, ko sabu ko sabu ko Joomi am wahayini e am kon, tawde pellet, ko o nanoowo, Ɓadiiɗo"."
  34,51,"Sinno a tinatno, tuma nde ɓe ɗeŋƴii, - laaworde alanaa (ɓe), - ɓe nanngiree e nokkuure ɓadiinde!"
  34,52,"Ɓe mbi'a: "Min ngooŋɗinii [Darngal] ngal", e ko holno gooŋɗinal woonirani ɓe e nokku goɗɗuɗo?"
  34,53,"Hara non ɓe jeddiino nde ko adii, heɓe mbernora ko wirnii e nokku goɗɗuɗo!"
  34,54,"Heedee hakkunde e ko ɓe tuuyetee, wano golliranoo e nanndo maɓɓe ko adii, tawde ɓe ngoniino e sikke cikkiniiɗa."
  35,1,"Jettooje ngoodanii Alla, Takɗo kammuuji ɗin e leydi ndin, baɗɗo Malaa'ikaaji nulaaɓe, marɓe gabitanji(bibje) ɗi ɗiɗi, ɗi tati e nayi. Homo ɓesda ko o muuyi e tagu makko ngun, tawde pellet, Alla ko kattanɗo kala hu'unde."
  35,2,"Kala yurmeende nde Alla udditani yimɓe ɓen, jogitotooɗo nde alaa; kala kadi ko o jogitii, gaccitoowo ɗum alaa ɓaawo (jogitagol) makko. Ko Kaŋko woni pooluɗo, ñeeñɗo."
  35,3,"Eey mon yo yimɓe! Njaŋtee neema Alla on e mon. Hara tagoowo ko woori Alla no woodi, mo no arsikira on ka kammu e ka leydi? Deweteeɗo alaa si wonaa Kaŋko! E ko honno njilirteɗon [e kaa goonga]?"